div.p:
The meeting was opened with a prayer by the Reverend Dr. William Goodell;
                        after which the chairman addressed it on the subject of the deplorable
                        occurrences which had called it together.

The Reverend Dr. William Goodell, chairman; Reverend Dr. Elias Riggs, member;
                        Dr. D. Stamatiades, member; Reverend George Washburn, member; Mr. John P.
                        Brown, secretary; who adopted the following:
